{"word":"βαδιστέος","slug":"βαδιστέος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>βαδιστέος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:verbal Adjective'>verb. <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a></a> of <a href='S:βαδίζω'><el>βαδίζω</el></a>\n<p/><i>one must walk</i> or <i>go</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>:—so <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <el>βαδιστέα</el>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/>"}]}